        <item>
            <title>Qualcomm 下周一举行发布会，料公布 Snapdragon 8s Gen3 等处理器</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/12/qualcomm-to-launch-new-snapdragon-chips-on-march-18-event-8s-gen-3-7-gen-3-expected/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=qualcomm-to-launch-new-snapdragon-chips-on-march-18-event-8s-gen-3-7-gen-3-expected</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/12/qualcomm-to-launch-new-snapdragon-chips-on-march-18-event-8s-gen-3-7-gen-3-expected/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[唐美凤]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 03:00:47 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[qualcomm]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Snapdragon 7+ Gen 3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Snapdragon 8s Gen 3]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1223744</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>昨日晶片商 Qualcomm 宣布将会在 3 月 18 日下午举行新品发布会，推出多款旗舰级处理器，今次发布会的口号为「智在芯中，有龙则灵」。有传闻指 Qualcomm 将会在发布会上，公布 Snapdragon 7+ Gen 3 (SM7675) 和 Snapdragon 8s Gen 3 (SM8635) 处理器。</p><p><span id="more-1223744"></span></p><p>两款处理器据悉代号同样为「Cliffs」，属同一核心架构的不同变体，预计架构与 Snapdragon 8 Gen 3 相同。根据早前的众多爆料，Snapdragon 7+ Gen 3 配备一枚 2.9GHz Cortex-X4 超大核、四枚 2.6GHz Cortex-A720 大核和三枚 1.9GHz Cortex-A520 节能核心，并搭配 Adreno 732 图像处理器。</p><p>至于 Snapdragon 8s Gen 3 的规格，则由一枚 3.01GHz Cortex-X4 超大核、四枚 2.61GHz Cortex-A720 大核和三枚 1.84GHz Cortex-A520 节能核心组成，图像处理器则为 Adreno 735。有指多间中国手机厂商，包括 Realme、红米、小米、OnePlus、vivo、iQOO 将会以这两款处理器推出新手机，预计 3 月 18 日发布会有更多详情。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2024/03/11/qualcomm-to-launch-new-snapdragon-chips-on-march-18-event-8s-gen-3-7-gen-3-expected/">gizmochina</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/snapdragon-x-elite-visits-geekbench/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Qualcomm 全新电脑处理器   Snapdragon X Elite 现身跑分网站</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/04/samsung-qualcomm-multi-year-deal-snapdragon-chips/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">与 Qualcomm 签订多年合约   Samsung 继续使用 Snapdragon 处理器</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/07/snapdragon-xr2-plus-gen-2-launched/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Snapdragon XR2+ Gen 2 发表   Qualcomm 为 Google、Samsung 特别开发</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/12/qualcomm-to-launch-new-snapdragon-chips-on-march-18-event-8s-gen-3-7-gen-3-expected/mobile-phone/">Qualcomm 下周一举行发布会，料公布 Snapdragon 8s Gen3 等处理器</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
